.TH WLA\-65C02 1 "November 2023" "WLA-DX 10.6" "WLA DX Assembler"
.SH NAME
wla\-65c02 \- WLA DX cross-assembler for the WDC 65C02
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B wla\-65c02
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.B \-o
.I output.o
.I source.asm
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B wla\-65c02
assembles WDC 65C02 source code to a WLA DX object file.
The 65C02 is an enhanced variant of the MOS 6502 used in the Apple IIc and BBC Master.
.PP
All WLA DX assemblers share an identical command-line interface.
For full option descriptions, examples, and a list of all supported CPU
architectures, see
.BR wla\-6502 (1).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR wla\-6502 (1),
.BR wlalink (1)
